data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Hinckley, Ohio! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 5-full-bath residence is nestled on 2.08 acres of pristine land. As you step inside, you are welcomed by a grand and expansive foyer that sets the tone for the elegance and luxury that awaits throughout this magnificent home. The main kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, boasting stainless steel appliances, maple wood cabinets, and stunning granite countertops. Maplewood flooring in the family room, kitchen, living room, and dining room. Entertain with ease in the spacious living room featuring a cozy gas fireplace. The first-floor master bedroom is a true sanctuary with a tray ceiling and an en-suite master bath that includes Travertine floors, granite counters, double sinks, a Jacuzzi tub, and a private door leading to a deck with picturesque views. Convenience abounds with a first-floor laundry room featuring maple cabinets and Corian countertops. The first-floor office is graced with oak flooring, offering a refined workspace within the comfort of home. All bedrooms are generous in size with large storage spaces. With a finished walkout basement complete with a full kitchen and a full bathroom, this home is an entertainer's dream. The property is equipped with a 15-zone sprinkler system. Fenced-in garden in. Spacious 3-car garage plus additional 1.5-car garage in the backyard. Shangle roof with 50 year warranty! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity. Schedule your showing today!
